ingredients.ingredient: 1 pound lean (at least 80%) ground beef, cooked, drained
1 (10.2 ounce) can Pillsbury® Grands!® Flaky Layers refrigerated biscuits

cookingTips: Press biscuits into muffin cups to create cup shape
Drain ground beef thoroughly to prevent soggy cups
Bake at 375°F for 12-15 minutes until biscuits are golden
enrichment.coachingPrompt: How can you ensure these cups are crispy on the outside while keeping the filling warm?
